result.name: Royal Dessert

reviews.text: Good taste. Reasonable price.

Not the most famous part of the city, but this dessert place was a good surprise. I tried the chocolate waffle. The waffle and ice cream had their own personnality and it was a pleasure to taste it. The price is between 25 and 50 HKD. The menu is colored and full of Asian and western delight and the service was quick.  I did not take risk for this first time but there is a long list of original dishes that deserve to be tested in the futur.
Good and tasty dessert, worthy to try
Awesome
Interesting dessert

result.name: 皇室甜品

reviews.text: 地方人少，靜，適合小休息，味道一流，但草苺味有点甜，價格有優惠，服務良好，但價格之間比重不公平。
芒果西米露 非常好 名不虛傳的甜品 而且桌子很多 不需排隊

榴槤公主 (甜品名稱) 夠香，加上坐底奶凍和粒粒啫喱，這組合非常好 !
喳咋都好足料啊，值得再食。
食品質素環境都好，價錢合理。
啲甜品幾好味，買相唔錯
